➜看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了…
https://www.uisdc.com/adobe-max-2020	60284
<p>当国内不少设计师们，努力盘算双十一买啥更省钱时，一年一度的设计界盛典AdobeMax正在大洋彼岸举办着</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393353" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-1.gif" width="550" height="227" /></span></p>
<p>虽说早在上个月，Ps2021测试版本就已经惨遭泄露，新的智能滤镜系统被扒得一干二净，却并不影响大家对这届Max的期待</p>
<p>因为长达1个半小时的创意者大会，总不能光讲个PS吧，Adobe全家桶究竟获得哪些新升级，让我们把话筒交给主持人一起听听看：</p>
<p>2020年，对设计师们而言，毫无疑问，是特别艰难的一年，往年去办公室打工，周围坐的是同事，现在坐办公室，满屋子都是新冠病毒。</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393354" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-2.jpg" width="625" height="351" /></span></p>
<p>我知道你们特别能忍，办公室不能待，那就走到大街上作图。</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393355" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-3.jpg" width="800" height="401" /></span></p>
<p>可问题是，今年马路牙子也不安全，满大街都是“黑命贵”挨一砖头事小，电脑砸烂了事儿大</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393356" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-4.jpg" width="625" height="352" /></span></p>
<p>说到底，问题都在于电脑设备太笨重，不能随时随地作图，所以今年的主题就是：让设计师全面进入——跑路P图时代</p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">Ai for iPad</span></h4>
<p>是的，是的！Ps登录iPad一年之后，我们把Ai也成功移植了！扔掉你的Mac，买一块iPad就够了！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393357" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-5.jpg" width="293" height="289" /></span></p>
<p>电脑上用Ai，还得挨个去勾锚点，在iPad上，我们有ApplePencil，小笔一挥，所画既所得！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393358" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-6.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>想用素材图案铺满一整个画面？别再一枚枚复制了！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393359" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-7.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>全新的智能平铺工具，铺满整个屏幕，花不了你5秒钟！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393360" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-8.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>画放射状图案，还在拿着量角器一根根找角度？</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393361" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-9.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>全新的旋转复制工具，要多圆有多圆，想要多少瓣就多少瓣</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393362" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-10.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>配色老大难？我们还有色卡着色系统，色卡不再是玄学而是真的可以为设计师所用！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393363" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-11.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>甚至还能从别的作品上吸配色！只要脸皮有够厚，大佬作品的配色就是你的配色！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393364" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-12.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>有了Ai for iPad，设计师就不用钉在桌子上作图，边走边打工，感染风险成倍降低</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393365" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-13.jpg" width="687" height="521" /></span></p>
<p>怎么，你都这么努力打工了</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393366" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-14.jpg" width="296" height="288" /></span></p>
<p>难道还买不起iPad &amp; Pencil？</p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">苹果手机P图三件套！</span></h4>
<p>很多人以为今年Ps2021提前曝光了，我们PS部门就没东西可讲了</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393367" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-15.jpg" width="266" height="263" /></span></p>
<p>笑话，除了Ps2021我们还开发出了手机P图三件套！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393368" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-16.jpg" width="1080" height="251" /></span></p>
<p>创意来了，掏出PsExpress 听上去就比X图秀秀更专业！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393369" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-17.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>智能抠图、内置图层系统，四舍五入就是手机版的PS啊！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393370" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-18.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>做海报，就用Spark Post 丰富版式仍你选，素材扔进去，十秒就出图</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393371" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-19.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>字体、字号、颜色，想换就换</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393372" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-20.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>给女朋友拍照，就用Ps Camera 照片不用往电脑上导，抓拍到了丑照，当场P完发朋友圈，原地分手，毫无痛苦</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393373" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-21.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>技术不够，滤镜凑，只要你够抗揍，就能把朋友P得，连他亲妈都不认得</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393374" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-22.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>想用上以上这些全新的P图软件，边走边P图？只要有部iPhone就够了！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393375" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-23.jpg" width="671" height="275" /></span></p>
<p>考虑到很多设计师买不起iPhone，我们勉为其难，也对Ps for iPad做了一些小更新</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393376" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-24.jpg" width="274" height="275" /></span></p>
<p>比如智能抠图功能、上线了曲线系统</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393377" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-25.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>但我还是更推荐你去买一部iPhone可比iPad贵轻多了！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393378" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-26.jpg" width="270" height="272" /></span></p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">手机版LightRoom</span></h4>
<p>你们发现没，Ai和Ps嘴上说便携可都是躲在家里拍只有我们Lr，才是真的移动便携！拍摄场地都在山里！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393379" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-27.jpg" width="625" height="349" /></span></p>
<p>以前用iPad调光，只能一整张去调高光压低，阴影煳了阴影稍微提亮一点，高光又过曝了</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393380" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-28.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>但Lr for iPad拥有高光、过渡、阴影三重分段，光影更细腻</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393381" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-29.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>还能选定区域，进行精确调整！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393382" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-30.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>或者反向操作，只调背景，突出主体以上这些新功能，安卓版(?)Lr都能用！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393383" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-31.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>想让你的照片变得更有逼格？</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393384" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-32.jpg" width="287" height="291" /></span></p>
<p>买一部安卓手机你就能用上可比iPhone便宜多了！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393385" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-33.jpg" width="1080" height="887" /></span></p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">Fresco智能笔刷</span></h4>
<p>当年Fr的水墨笔刷一经推出不少设计师就在惊呼，简直是魔法</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393386" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-34.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>你们真是少见多怪今天让你看看什么才是真正的魔法</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393387" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-35.jpg" width="258" height="255" /></span></p>
<p>随便找一张素材，摁住</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393388" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-36.jpg" width="625" height="349" /></span></p>
<p>它就是你的个性笔刷了！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393389" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-37.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>给斑马画花纹也不必小心翼翼</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393390" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-38.gif" width="611" height="349" /></span></p>
<p>随便涂几笔，摁住，画道删除线，超出边框的条纹，就能被识别出来，删得干干净净</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393391" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-39.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>作图的效率是不是翻了几番？买一部iPhone手指就是你的魔法棒！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393392" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-40.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<h4><span class="auto_menu">Pr动态捕捉&amp;自动生成字幕</span></h4>
<p>现在TikTok很火害得视频统统都要剪成竖屏的这就给剪辑师带来很大的麻烦</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393393" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-41.jpg" width="250" height="241" /></span></p>
<p>你比方说这个视频，狗狗很可爱但如果做成竖屏，就得加个蒙版</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393394" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-42.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>可这蒙版一加，问题也就来了狗呢？狗不见了，以前只能靠手动挪镜头来解决</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393395" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-43.jpg" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>现在有了Pr“智能跟随”工具不论主体怎么跑，都能随时处在镜头的正中央</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393396" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-44.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>除了做跟踪，字幕也是个大工程，光打字都要花半天，现在这一切，统统扔给Pr自己弄！</p>
<p>自动听写带时间轴的字幕文件，往视频里一拖，字幕就完成了</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393397" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-45.gif" width="608" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>这么方便的功能，究竟iPhone和安卓那边的用户能先用上呢？</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393398" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-46.jpg" width="248" height="247" /></span></p>
<p>两边都没得用，想屁吃，电脑上才有Pr</p>
