<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="看完Adobe Max 2020，80%的设计师都把Mac砸了&#8230;" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-393399" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uisdc-my-20201025-47.jpg" width="625" height="350" /></span></p>
